data.title: Emergency Bill Allows 11th Street Bridge Park To Proceed
data.meta_description: The 11th Street Bridge Park, planned to be built on old pilings spanning the Anacostia River, hit a last minute permitting snag, but is now cleared for construction to begin next year.
